        "ggO4UrlMw9D_label": "<p>Limited Time: Free Milk Frother Included</p>",
        "ggY3GV6fDaJ_text": "<p>Teangle didn’t start as a business idea.<br>It started as a search for balance.</p><p><br>For years, I struggled with anxiety and energy crashes — chasing focus with coffee, then paying for it later. At the same time, I watched my mom spend her life taking care of everyone else… rarely herself.</p><p><br>What we needed wasn’t more stimulation.<br>We needed steadiness.</p><p><br>That’s where Teangle was born — inspired by the triangle, a symbol of balance. Mind. Body. Ritual.</p><p><br>We created a simple daily ritual designed to bring calm energy and support from within — without the crash, without the overwhelm.<br>Because self-care shouldn’t be another task.</p><p><br>It should be something you look forward to.</p>",
        "ggcpY3s2Ogw_text": "Our Mission"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-609005170650514180"
    },
