        "ggMhw-EDaTr_text": "FAQs",
        "ggTJ001QG7P_text": "<p>Yes. Many customers switch from coffee to Vanilla Matcha Collagen because it delivers steady, focused energy without jitters or crashes. It’s a smoother alternative to traditional caffeine.</p>",
